Dialogs.Dialog: Well, maybe it's just my imagination...
I feel like I've had fewer emails lately. Are you avoiding me?
...Maybe we are in a period of boredom?
Is that the case for me too? But I haven't been sending you much email lately.
That's right. There's nothing I can do about it anymore.
you know what. I feel like the number of emails is decreasing...
Because I'm waiting every day. If I don't send you more emails... I'll be gonna squeal?
I'm not bored with me, right?
Sorry. I feel like I've been kissing less and less.
...I think so. Just because you're not kissing doesn't mean you don't like me.
Hey, haven't you been cold lately?
Oh, I don't think that's the case...
But he's not kissing me much lately.
Or is there anything wrong with me?
Hey, do you notice? Something we lack these days.
...Kiss. It doesn't do that much, does it?
Don't let me say this too much...
I've broken my date promises several times. Why?
It's not that I don't like meeting me.
Is that so? Is it because of ●?
There's no way you don't think you'll ever think about it after going on dates many times, right?
Are you really reflecting on it? yeah?
Hey, there's something to talk about, is it okay?
At this point, they don't keep their promises properly. I look forward to every date.
I wouldn't want to say this if possible. You know.
(I have to make you angry any more)
Hey, I'd like to talk a little.
I was left alone on the other day. ...Has something happened?
...Don't do it anymore. Because it makes me sad.
(It looks like he's in a bad mood, that's true.)
The last date. I've been silent forever.
What's wrong? Leave your girlfriend alone all the time during the date.
Are you okay? I... I want to see you more.
Hey, how can I meet more?
(It seems to make me feel a little lonely...)
What do you think about us these days?
What do you think... what do you mean?
I don't think we've seen them very often.
I would like to see more if possible... that's what I think.
Um... I want to see you more.
You're meeting like this now, right?
That's right, but... I haven't seen them very often lately.
This is sad. I want to meet more and more...
The girl from before... a friend?
Well, I'm just a normal friend though. Did you notice?
Just a little bit. But it's just a little bit. I don't care.
(It seems like he's a bit worried...)
He's been pretty close to the person he used to.
Is that so? I'm just a normal friend though.
Yes... I wonder if I'm too concerned about it?
Who is the girl now? They seemed to be good friends though.
They're just friends, but...▲Anegasaki*▲, are you jealous?
Is it likely to cure your cold?
Because I think that cold was transmitted from ●?
Hmm... I don't know. Don't worry, that's what it is.
He doesn't look like that. If you take good rest, it will get better.
Perhaps that's the case. But you don't have to worry about that.
It's fine... It'll get better soon if you take a break.
sorry. Did you get that cold from ●?
Don't apologize. Because I don't think it's your fault.
I want to take responsibility. The cold will be brought home.
Give that cold back. Will you be fine then?
already. There's no end, if you do that.
Please attach it to ●. Because of ●, ▲Anegasaki*▲ is...
...Rejected. I don't want you to suffer. I should fix it properly.
I don't apologize...but I'm somehow happy.
It's good. Instead, when you feel better, why not play a lot?
Don't face that cute. Your sister's fever will rise, right?
Oh yeah, I had cut an apple. Can you eat it?
Will that make me eat it?
OK, it's fine. Keep your posture comfortable.
Thank you for visiting me today. Thanks to that, it will soon he will heal.
Yeah. So ● will be back soon. I'll wait for you to get better.
It's already completely. Sorry for your concern.
That's good...but I couldn't come and visit you.
That's fine. I didn't let it go to you. hey.
(Even if you're worried about ●...I should have come and visited him.)
I managed to do something myself because you wouldn't come and visit me.
joke. I don't want to show my weakness.
(But after all, he would be happy when he went...)
Are you okay with a cold now?
That's good... I was thinking of going to visit you, but before that it got better.
Ah, that's a shame. I wish you'd take care of me.
I was revived after you cheered me up.
That's good...it looks like I'm feeling well.
It's a treat. Was you okay after that?
Ah, no problem. Tell me when you have a cold again.
Do you kiss me every time you get a cold? That might be... good too.
Good, it looks like I'm feeling well.
This is thanks to you after all.
I won't say that straightforward anymore.
Hey, isn't it painful to talk to me? Are you okay?
Are you okay. Rather, it's getting more energy.
Your cold...Can I try to see if I can spread it to me and get rid of it?
▲Anegasaki*▲, do you want to transfer it?
Are you feeling sick? You have to sleep properly.
He's not a child, so he's sleeping quietly.
A cold looks like it's going to be tough. Shall I try and see if I can take it home?
picture? Will you bring it home?
Please fix it quickly... I've been worried about you forever.
thank you. Please don't get sick to ▲Anegasaki*▲.
Hey...Didn't a cold go away if you kiss him? try out?
Yes... I'll give it a try.
I was meant to be kidding... so let's try it, right?
Whether it's true, you have to give it a try, right?
I agree. Shall I do that?
...I think this has made me feel better.
ah. I feel like I'm gaining some strength.
good. So that means I've got a cold.
good. So, if I catch a cold from this, why don't you take care of me like I am now?
It's no good if it's spread. ▲Anegasaki*▲ collapses.
What are you talking about? If you don't spread, you won't be able to heal.
Get rid of your cold quickly. please.
▲Anegasaki*▲ too... don't let the cold get caught.
I know. You can't go on a date unless you're both healthy.
Yes...thank you. I feel like my body is lighter.
me too. Has the cold gone somewhere?
Not that... I suddenly started to feel embarrassed.
That's not good. ▲Anegasaki*▲ will have a cold, right?
I'm fine with that... yes, I understand.
That's not possible, that's it. Even if it's spread, it won't cure.
Hmm... I guess that's what it is.
Is it a superstition... I guess so after all.
Is your stomach okay? I made porridge...
I can eat it. I'll eat it!
Thank you for visiting me, I'm feeling energized!
good. So I guess I'll be excuse soon. Take a good rest until it's completely healed.
Isn't it too much? Has it really been healed?
As you can see, he's in good spirits.
That's good... I've been worried for a long time.
It's not that exaggerated. thank you for worrying about me.
Congratulations on your return. Are you okay now?
ah. It wasn't a very bad cold in the first place.
I see, as long as you're so energetic, I guess it's okay if you don't let him be spoiled.
I'm glad it got better... I was worried.
thank you. Because there's nothing more.
Even if we didn't meet, I'll let you be so spoiled.
My cold has been cured perfectly. ▲Thanks to Anegasaki*▲.
I wonder if it was worth visiting.
By the way... is that okay? You may have a cold or something...
I? It's okay, it seems I didn't get any depression.
Finally, my cold has gone away.
Yes, that's good. Is it the effect of my visit?
Oh yeah, thank you for that time. ...After that, what about ▲Anegasaki*▲?
▲Anegasaki*▲ helped me get rid of my cold properly.
good. The kiss from that time worked.
That's right... so it's going to fall over there...
Are you okay. I didn't get a cold either.
(▲Anegasaki*▲, maybe a little different from usual?)
You might be surprised if you said something like this...
What... of course, about you. No way?
It's not bad, but... I'm not surprised, that's obvious.
It's obvious, but... it's not obvious. Because...
I love it so much...it's different from usual.
Sorry, you're saying something weird...I'm a bit weird...
I love it so much that it makes me go crazy...
(▲Anegasaki*▲, what's going on... is it angry?)
...It's decided, isn't it? I love it, I love it. I really like it!
My face is hot...it looks like it's going to explode...
What do you mean, what is the current ▲Anegasaki*▲...
No... I don't want to hear it. When I hear it, it really explodes...
If it's banned, then no longer!
(▲Anegasaki*▲, he was more aggressive than usual...)
